610
00:49:15,599 --> 00:49:17,660
Who should I be happy for?

611
00:49:30,260 --> 00:49:32,240
What's wrong with you?

612
00:49:38,340 --> 00:49:43,100
Does your birthday bring up bad memories for you?

613
00:49:45,520 --> 00:49:48,840
It's not healthy to bottle up your feelings.

614
00:49:48,840 --> 00:49:52,100
If you're upset about something, say it out loud.

615
00:49:53,320 --> 00:49:55,420
This might make you feel better.

616
00:49:56,879 --> 00:49:58,800
Do you want to know?

617
00:50:08,940 --> 00:50:10,920
Who do you think you are?

618
00:50:14,920 --> 00:50:17,040
Why should I tell you?

619
00:50:23,715 --> 00:50:25,540
Are you not going to leave?

620
00:50:28,200 --> 00:50:29,740
I'll leave.

621
00:51:41,380 --> 00:51:43,530
Stop pretending!

622
00:51:43,530 --> 00:51:45,740
Let's team up!

623
00:51:45,740 --> 00:51:48,270
Team up? Okay, fine!

624
00:51:48,270 --> 00:51:51,680
