734
01:00:50,200 --> 01:00:53,420
Even if he hadn't told me what was going on,

735
01:00:53,420 --> 01:00:58,320
I would have still been okay if he had just hugged me and said something nice.

736
01:01:00,360 --> 01:01:02,740
But you know what?

737
01:01:03,280 --> 01:01:06,600
Even after I tossed the cake onto the floor,

738
01:01:07,500 --> 01:01:10,220
he didn't say anything.

739
01:01:10,220 --> 01:01:12,460
It was such a nice cake.

740
01:01:13,700 --> 01:01:15,300
It must've taken her a long time to make it.

741
01:01:15,300 --> 01:01:18,320
I spent so much time learning how to make it.

742
01:01:18,320 --> 01:01:22,840
My parents gained three pounds just from eating my practice cakes,

743
01:01:22,840 --> 01:01:26,000
and it ended up getting tossed to the floor.

744
01:01:26,620 --> 01:01:28,960
She made it herself

745
01:01:28,960 --> 01:01:31,620
and then, just threw it away so cruelly.

746
01:01:31,620 --> 01:01:34,000
I didn't even get to eat a single bite of it.

747
01:01:46,140 --> 01:01:49,180
Stop drinking. Stop drinking.

748
01:01:56,680 --> 01:02:01,640
When your efforts fail to enter the other person's heart.

749
01:02:02,600 --> 01:02:05,120
They ferment and turn into depression.

750
01:02:07,640 --> 01:02:11,420
You think that you can drown your sorrows with drinks,

751
01:02:11,420 --> 01:02:13,840
but it just causes an even deeper depression.

752
01:02:20,940 --> 01:02:23,020
I want to eat the cake.

753
01:02:36,160 --> 01:02:39,580
If you have anything on your mind, it's best to just speak up.

754
01:02:41,320 --> 01:02:43,800
Why do I have to speak about it?

755
01:02:44,720 --> 01:02:47,100
Can't you just stay with me for a little while?

756
01:02:48,160 --> 01:02:51,200
Sure, I'll stay with you.

757
01:03:27,040 --> 01:03:28,700
Mom,

758
01:03:28,700 --> 01:03:32,440
Meng Meng and her husband had a little fight.

759
01:03:32,440 --> 01:03:35,780
She doesn't want her parents to know so she's going to stay with me tonight.

760
01:03:36,520 --> 01:03:37,840
Were you drinking as well?

761
01:03:37,840 --> 01:03:41,420
Just a little to keep her company.

762
01:03:41,420 --> 01:03:44,960
Don't worry. Don't you have dialysis tomorrow? Get some sleep. Don't worry about us.

763
01:03:44,960 --> 01:03:46,660
Bye bye.

764
01:03:56,860 --> 01:03:59,320
Here, put this on.

765
01:04:30,340 --> 01:04:33,980
That day when you left and came back and wouldn't stop drinking,

766
01:04:34,000 --> 01:04:37,820
was it because you were also trying to drown out something that you couldn't put into words?

767
01:04:37,820 --> 01:04:39,880
You wanted to drown it out.

768
01:04:39,880 --> 01:04:42,960
