773
01:05:41,940 --> 01:05:44,280
Meng Meng hasn't called me all night!

774
01:05:44,280 --> 01:05:47,180
Is she really angry enough to leave me?

775
01:05:47,180 --> 01:05:48,600
She's...

776
01:05:49,840 --> 01:05:52,260
just like that cake.

777
01:05:56,320 --> 01:06:00,580
She's ignoring me right now. What should I do?

778
01:06:00,580 --> 01:06:03,160
Why is she still ignoring me?

779
01:06:03,160 --> 01:06:07,080
Why is she ignoring me?

780
01:06:07,080 --> 01:06:09,600
It's been a whole night.

781
01:06:09,600 --> 01:06:13,660
Is she really ignoring me? She's really something else.

782
01:06:18,740 --> 01:06:22,860
Well... Teach me how to cook after work today.

783
01:06:22,860 --> 01:06:26,120
I don't have any objections to the theme of this episode.

784
01:06:26,940 --> 01:06:30,260
I'll pay you extra for the lesson and overtime.

785
01:06:33,000 --> 01:06:36,820
Are you feeling bad for what you did last night and looking for an excuse to talk to her?

786
01:06:36,820 --> 01:06:39,000
Mind your own business.

787
01:06:41,700 --> 01:06:43,620
I asked for a day off today.

788
01:06:50,270 --> 01:06:52,640
[Internal Medicine Clinic - Room 6]

789
01:06:52,640 --> 01:06:56,740
Doctor Wang, my mom's creatinine index increased by 3.7.

790
01:06:56,740 --> 01:06:58,800
Is that going to be a problem?

791
01:06:58,800 --> 01:07:03,360
It's all right. It'll come down after dialysis.

792
01:07:03,360 --> 01:07:05,420
Thank you, Doctor Wang.

793
01:07:05,420 --> 01:07:08,480
Kelan is really attentive.

794
01:07:09,000 --> 01:07:11,060
Go and get the dialysis done first.

795
01:07:11,060 --> 01:07:14,740
Okay, wait for me, Mom. I'll go pay the fees.

796
01:07:14,740 --> 01:07:18,180
By the way, here.

797
01:07:18,180 --> 01:07:19,620
What is it this time?

798
01:07:19,620 --> 01:07:23,280
Strawberry Jam, your granddaughter's favorite.

799
01:07:23,280 --> 01:07:25,740
She really loves this.

800
01:07:25,740 --> 01:07:27,920
She has eaten so much that she has cavities now.

801
01:07:30,520 --> 01:07:32,360
One appointment is only ¥800.

802
01:07:32,360 --> 01:07:35,280
Ma'am, judging by your outfit, you must have just returned from abroad.

803
01:07:35,280 --> 01:07:40,380
It's okay if you don't know me, but you must go to Dr. Li for the Thermage Treatment.
(T/N: Thermage is a skin tightening treatment.)

804
01:07:40,380 --> 01:07:45,160
It's really difficult to get an appointment. I'm quite sure that they don't have any slots available for this week.

805
01:07:45,160 --> 01:07:47,140
Well,

806
01:07:47,140 --> 01:07:48,400
what should I do then?

807
01:07:48,400 --> 01:07:50,280
Look, so many people are lining up over there.

808
01:07:50,280 --> 01:07:53,460
If you line up like them, you may not be able to get one.

809
01:07:53,460 --> 01:07:57,020
Instead, you can just pay ¥800 to save your time and effort.

810
01:07:57,020 --> 01:07:58,880
Ma'am, it's not expensive at all.

811
01:07:58,880 --> 01:08:00,520
Just ¥800,

812
01:08:00,520 --> 01:08:02,180
- buy it from me.
- Fine.

813
01:08:02,180 --> 01:08:05,100
- Come on, buy one.
- Auntie,

814
01:08:06,120 --> 01:08:08,800
the Cosmetology Department's appointments aren't hard to get.

815
01:08:08,800 --> 01:08:11,760
Just follow the official account of this hospital.

816
01:08:11,760 --> 01:08:15,080
Look, you can book an appointment right here.

817
01:08:19,680 --> 01:08:21,820
Miss, Thank you so much.

818
01:08:21,820 --> 01:08:24,520
I almost got scammed by him.

819
01:08:24,520 --> 01:08:26,880
You're welcome.

820
01:08:26,880 --> 01:08:28,580
Kelan!

821
01:08:31,200 --> 01:08:32,700
Kelan!

822
01:08:35,280 --> 01:08:37,780
- Hello?
- Mom, are you back?

823
01:08:37,780 --> 01:08:39,480
Why didn't you let me pick you up?

824
01:08:39,480 --> 01:08:42,000
It's okay. I'll be home soon.

825
01:08:42,000 --> 01:08:45,400
Call Yu Hao and ask him to come over for dinner.

826
01:08:45,400 --> 01:08:49,840
Kelan! Kelan, don't go! Kelan!

827
01:08:53,560 --> 01:08:55,080
Don't touch it.

828
01:08:57,100 --> 01:08:59,020
Kelan, don't overthink it.

829
01:08:59,020 --> 01:09:02,660
My mom and I came here to see your mom today.

830
01:09:02,660 --> 01:09:05,840
Didn't I always accompany your mom for dialysis before?

831
01:09:05,840 --> 01:09:07,560
Three times.

832
01:09:09,980 --> 01:09:12,320
My mom gets dialysis done twice a week.

833
01:09:12,320 --> 01:09:17,210
We were together for five years. That's 520 times. You only came three times.

834
01:09:17,920 --> 01:09:22,140
We already broke up. Don't you ever get tired of putting on a show?

835
01:09:23,440 --> 01:09:25,100
Kelan,

836
01:09:25,100 --> 01:09:27,520
I know that I didn't do well in the past.

837
01:09:27,520 --> 01:09:30,240
It's all my fault. I won't make any excuses.

838
01:09:30,240 --> 01:09:35,280
I deserve to be dumped and fired.

839
01:09:35,280 --> 01:09:38,880
But I've really been thinking about you all this time.

840
01:09:38,880 --> 01:09:40,940
I can't get over you.

841
01:09:40,940 --> 01:09:44,180
I really regret not being there for you and your mom.

842
01:09:44,180 --> 01:09:47,740
Then be there for your mom, your current girlfriend, and your future girlfriends.

843
01:09:47,740 --> 01:09:51,180
- Don't regret it again.
- Kelan, I've realized that I was wrong.

844
01:09:51,180 --> 01:09:53,700
I know that you won't forgive me.

845
01:09:53,700 --> 01:09:55,620
I'm not asking that we get back together.

846
01:09:55,620 --> 01:09:57,920
But we've been together for so many years.

847
01:09:57,920 --> 01:10:00,580
Even if we break up, can't we just be friends?

848
01:10:00,580 --> 01:10:02,740
Why should I be friends with you?

849
01:10:04,160 --> 01:10:06,960
You know that I don't like to drag things out.

850
01:10:06,960 --> 01:10:10,520
I'll live my own life, and so should you.

851
01:10:10,520 --> 01:10:12,440
One last word of advice.

852
01:10:12,440 --> 01:10:15,840
Be more sincere and loyal.

853
01:10:15,840 --> 01:10:18,200
Otherwise, you will end up with nothing.

854
01:10:18,840 --> 01:10:20,800
Kelan,

855
01:10:20,800 --> 01:10:23,200
I still have feelings for you.

856
01:10:27,020 --> 01:10:30,200
Some people can't appreciate your good intentions.

857
01:10:30,200 --> 01:10:33,620
Let's go. Let's go.

858
01:10:43,240 --> 01:10:46,540
- Did you get it?
- Yes, I did.

859
01:10:52,540 --> 01:10:55,040
The passcode is still the same.

860
01:11:10,380 --> 01:11:13,260
Stand there. Don't move. Let me adjust this.

861
01:11:13,260 --> 01:11:16,110
I'm making scrambled eggs with tomatoes.

862
01:11:16,980 --> 01:11:20,120
I'm recording it so that you can review it later on.

863
01:11:38,290 --> 01:11:43,930
♫  Who's hiding in a corner of their memories, talking to themselves?  ♫

864
01:11:43,930 --> 01:11:49,294
♫  In the void of the night, no one answers.  ♫

865
01:11:49,294 --> 01:11:53,514
♫  The moment the wind blows, it awakens me from my fatigue  ♫

866
01:11:53,514 --> 01:11:59,414
♫  Looking at the city lights, I feel the contrast with reality  ♫

867
01:11:59,414 --> 01:12:05,454
♫  But I still have to go down this road  ♫

868
01:12:05,454 --> 01:12:11,794
♫  Upon taking a step further, will my dream develop into something more? ♫

869
01:12:11,794 --> 01:12:14,734
♫  In this world full of fireworks, I see unexpected changes  ♫

870
01:12:14,734 --> 01:12:17,594
♫  I feel reluctant to be swept away by the scenery  ♫

871
01:12:17,594 --> 01:12:21,154
♫  How many more journeys will I undergo before I'm left astounded and speechless?  ♫

872
01:12:21,154 --> 01:12:23,134
♫  Experiencing all this heartache  ♫

873
01:12:23,134 --> 01:12:25,914
♫  As far as the eyes can see, sometimes it feels like I'm stranded  ♫

874
01:12:25,914 --> 01:12:28,734
♫  When I see my future self  ♫

875
01:12:28,734 --> 01:12:31,134
♫  Only then can I understand why I'm moving forward  ♫

876
01:12:31,134 --> 01:12:35,014
♫  I will still be as stubborn as I've always been  ♫

877
01:12:45,380 --> 01:12:48,114
♫  The uncertain suspense of this world  ♫

878
01:12:48,114 --> 01:12:51,094
♫  Who has never cried their eyes out before?  ♫

879
01:12:51,094 --> 01:12:54,634
♫  Self-reflection will diminish what may come tomorrow  ♫

880
01:12:54,634 --> 01:12:56,534
♫  Let's reconcile with yesterday  ♫

881
01:12:56,534 --> 01:12:59,354
♫  When the raindrops will sigh and cover the glimmer of the starry sky ♫

882
01:12:59,354 --> 01:13:02,254
♫  I will look forward to the sunny days coming soon after  ♫

883
01:13:02,254 --> 01:13:04,414
♫  Let's stop and look up to see if we're still moving forward together  ♫

884
01:13:04,414 --> 01:13:08,694
♫  Is our pace the same as before?  ♫
